/**
 * Standardized Scale Definitions
 *
 * Each scale has been validated in Chinese populations with published reliability.
 * Items are fixed — NOT generated by AI. AI is only used for final recommendations.
 *
 * Sources:
 * - CBF-PI-B: 王孟成等(2011), 中国大五人格量表简版, α=0.769
 * - GSES: Schwarzer & Jerusalem 中文版一般自我效能感量表, α=0.87
 * - DASS-21: Lovibond & Lovibond 中文版抑郁-焦虑-压力量表, 压力子量表 α=0.76
 * - Growth Mindset: Dweck 隐含智力理论量表中文改编, α=0.80
 * - SGPS: Steel 一般拖延量表中文版, α=0.82
 * - ATMD: Britton & Tesser 时间管理倾向量表中文改编, α=0.84
 */

